Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.50,0:09:05.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.30,0:03:32.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳聞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.20,0:09:02.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我自己找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.90,0:09:04.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以吧
